  "content": "ipeline --nocapture`\nExpected: PASS\n\n**Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/corvia-kernel/src/lib.rs crates/corvia-kernel/src/rag_pipeline.rs\ngit commit -m \"feat(m3.2): create_rag_pipeline factory — auto-selects retriever from capabilities\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 9: REST Endpoints — /v1/context and /v1/ask\n\nAdd RAG endpoints to the REST server and fix existing search to route through the pipeline.\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-server/src/rest.rs`\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-server/Cargo.toml` (if needed for new deps)\n\n**Step 1: Add RagPipeline to AppState**\n\nIn `crates/corvia-server/src/rest.rs`, update `AppState`:\n\n```rust\npub struct AppState {\n    pub store: Arc<dyn QueryableStore>,\n    pub engine: Arc<dyn InferenceEngine>,\n    pub coordinator: Option<Arc<AgentCoordinator>>,\n    pub rag: Option<Arc<corvia_kernel::rag_pipeline::RagPipeline>>,\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Add request/response types**\n\nAdd after the existing DTO types:\n\n```rust\n#[derive(Deserialize)]\npub struct RagRequest {\n    pub query: String,\n    pub scope_id: String,\n    pub limit: Option<usize>,\n    pub expand_graph: Option<bool>,\n}\n\n#[derive(Serialize)]\npub struct RagResponseDto {\n    pub answer: Option<String>,\n    pub sources: Vec<SearchResultDto>,\n    pub trace: corvia_kernel::rag_types::PipelineTrace,",
